spec_data.Name: netpbm-doc
spec_data.License: BSD and GPLv2 and IJG and MIT and Public Domain
spec_data.Description:
The netpbm-doc package contains a documentation in HTML format for utilities
present in netpbm-progs package.

If you need to look into the HTML documentation, you should install
netpbm-doc.  You'll also need to install the netpbm-progs package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 08:04:19 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Documentation for tools manipulating graphics files in netpbm supported formats
